{"about_the_game":"<strong>READ THIS BEFORE YOU BUY!</strong><br><strong><i>The Chronicler</i> is in a very early stage of development. Please make sure to read the Early Access Q&amp;A above before buying.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614620/extras/lib3.png?t=1714648743\" /><br><br>A peculiar fantasy Open-World RPG where you are the author of your own adventure.<br><br><i>Immerse yourself in the enigmatic world of Isola Benedicta, a piece of land lost in the middle of the ocean, trapped in a power struggle between two factions after the discovery of a mysterious monolith. Embark on many adventures, fight mythical and dangerous creatures, meet peculiar characters, develop your abilities, and use your skills in battle, whether alone or with help from one of the many companions you'll encounter. You choose the battles that will define your story. After all, you are a Chronicler!</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614620/extras/5.png?t=1714648743\" /><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br>- Advance your Chronicler's skills by fighting monsters, cooking delicious meals, fishing, and exploring the huge map<br>- A variety of quests to test your ingenuity, from simple fetch quests to complex adventures<br>- Gorgeous, unique 2D pixel art and detailed animations<br>- Atmospheric original soundtrack and immersive sound effects<br>- Experience medieval life in the game's evocative environments<br><br>Enjoy the journey and write your own experience!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614620/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1714648743","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614620/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1714648743","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614620/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1714648743",